{"tid":1526064,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"警方：示威者在太子站內襲擊市民","createTime":"2019-09-01T04:08:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-01T05:00:56.000Z","uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"1121b46f3b85c1641232408ebf477a6e06bb6386","tid":1526064,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T04:08:20.000Z","msg":"警方嚴厲譴責激進示威者在港鐵內暴力行為<br />\n<br />\n＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊<br />\n<br />\n電台及電視台當值宣布員注意：<br />\n<br />\n請盡快播出下列消息，並在適當時間重播：<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n　　有激進暴力示威者，在港鐵旺角站衝擊客戶服務中心及毀壞售票機。<span style=\"color: red;\">示威者亦在港鐵太子站內襲擊市民</span>，毀壞站內設施。<br />\n　　&nbsp;<br />\n　　警方接報進入港鐵範圍制止暴力行為及拘捕違法者，呼籲在場市民立即離開。<br />\n　　&nbsp;<br />\n　　警方對示威者一切暴力行為，予以嚴厲譴責。&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n完<br />\n<br />\n2019年8月31日（星期六）<br />\n香港時間23時52分"},{"pid":"d2e98036ed85ae490477438373cf5b8370e99be3","tid":1526064,"uid":88937,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T04:09:40.000Z","msg":"係黑警係太子站內襲擊巿民"},{"pid":"063fa1264f45f2587d2b0ff8c2fdebf194cda833","tid":1526064,"uid":3073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T04:11:01.000Z","msg":"901 機場攻略<br />\n麻煩大家用盡所有方法傳開佢<br />\n<br />\n- <span style=\"color: red;\">準時</span>到機場，唔係一點先出門口<br />\n- 衣着同裝備冇任何限制，最緊要保護自己<br />\n- 集合地點：機場巴士總站(暢達路)<br />\n- 測試方法：排隊戰術，見到<span style=\"color: red;\">有隊就排</span>；利用人數優勢，<span style=\"color: red;\">唔好單獨行事</span><br />\n- 唔好同任何遊客有肢體碰撞<br />\n- 去機場：<span style=\"color: red;\">以巴士為優先</span>，機場快線集中係香港同青衣站上車<br />\n- 已經準備左幾套應變方案，根據現場情況<span style=\"color: red;\">隨時轉變</span>，要密切留意住 901 機場 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=dE5eED8%2BMjLqHtNzOSR2X4tKjO%2FIGoH7AJS0Ocrd4mI%3D&h=ad14be00\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/P5XusdO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FP5XusdO.jpg&h=31adcd48&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cTXKf68.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcTXKf68.jpg&h=74d57433&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qAxaV7a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqAxaV7a.jpg&h=13c2eb06&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/otZAnNa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FotZAnNa.jpg&h=f10fa124&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a2dbb499de16519ebff41e94806fe3d02b80c5d9","tid":1526064,"uid":131875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T05:00:56.000Z","msg":"大陸化<br />\n將黑白顛倒"}]}